{"tid":2388672,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬賽球迷真勇武","createTime":"2021-01-31T10:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T11:53:22.000Z","uid":136226,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4a3c4d23669d60330127eafc2ccdb565bb1c6102","tid":2388672,"uid":136226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:06:39.000Z","msg":"一批法甲球隊馬賽的球迷，因為不滿球隊近期戰績欠佳，到球隊訓練場地示威，有人向場地投擲煙霧彈，警方拘捕至少25人。 <br />\n<br />\n數百名馬賽球迷，周六手持煙霧彈到馬賽的訓練場地，多人向場內投擲煙霧彈，有樹木和建築物著火，部分人更試圖衝入訓練場。當時正在訓練場內的後衛艾華路蘇比朗，被球迷投擲的物體擊中受傷。<br />\n<br />\n馬賽原訂周六在主場迎戰雷恩的賽事宣布延期。馬賽發表聲明，譴責球迷襲擊球會的行為野蠻和不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CKrtMUKlmvW/?igshid=pd158a1qbwkn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCKrtMUKlmvW%2F%3Figshid%3Dpd158a1qbwkn&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWk2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=96d55d39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCKrtMUKlmvW%2F%3Figshid%3Dpd158a1qbwkn&h=30b87fae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CKrtMUKlmvW/?igshid=pd158a1qbwkn</a>"},{"pid":"0f8f33fc6d4ffe6a6ca50c8a652640d09b75343e","tid":2388672,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:07:05.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f97d2ef5d121088f90d1748922ad99d30bd1f0","tid":2388672,"uid":136226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:07:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661a1cd161f24bcdf9000f2741f656df65a71fef","tid":2388672,"uid":136226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0f8f33fc6d4ffe6a6ca50c8a652640d09b75343e","tid":2388672,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:07:05.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:07:17.000Z","msg":"法國手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce0e9a5ec7c870ba779b5168ab6838a72734c82","tid":2388672,"uid":136226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JtZbTD1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtZbTD1.jpg&h=186f35ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">從網上流傳的片段可見，一群馬賽球迷拉着寫有「董事們下台」的抗議橫額，並點起紅色煙火，一邊喊着口號、一邊朝着馬賽訓練場進發。<br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e96ef2ac74a386b131fea65ece8a7f19933e2aec","tid":2388672,"uid":43861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:09:18.000Z","msg":"Avb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f2fe5c7dadfc72c712bc1b1d84ff31bf1b2536","tid":2388672,"uid":136226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e96ef2ac74a386b131fea65ece8a7f19933e2aec","tid":2388672,"uid":43861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:09:18.000Z","msg":"Avb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:10:04.000Z","msg":"都係教唔掂 仲話咩新摩連奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af228ba0a2f3861fcb501e317521825c686d97d4","tid":2388672,"uid":136226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:13:56.000Z","msg":"文丹達比搞唔掂班球迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae92cef2aaaa3528876a73f18a1f04ca79f8502","tid":2388672,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T10:15:57.000Z","msg":"物理焦土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d9a6a25a0e12e168671a897e931923907f7c73","tid":238